@node "INSTALL" "Installation Instructions ;)"
                               @{b}INSTALLATION:@{ub}

 Copy 'WBStartup/StartupPlus' to the 'WBStartup' drawer
 Copy 'Prefs/SUPPrefs' to the 'Prefs' drawer
 Copy 'Libs/dospath.library' to 'Libs:'
 Copy 'Libs/wbstart.library' to 'Libs:'
 Copy 'SUPKeyFile' to 'ENV:' and 'ENVARC:'
 Copy 'StartupPlus.guide' to 'Help:'
 Copy 'SUPPrefs.guide' to 'Help:'

 or you can do it the simple way. This way will remove any old copies of
 the program it finds and install the new version. It leaves the icons if
 it findes them. Saves you editing the icons again. A little bit of P 'n' P
 for you. @{b}Just double click on the Install Icon.@{ub}

 With version 1.5 of StartupPlus you will have to install the Locale Catalog
 files manually. (I'm too lazy :) but have have coded a translater for the
 datafile into SUPPrefs.

 @{b}How to use:@{ub}
 @{" StartupPlus " link "STARTUPPLUS" 0}

