@node "HISTORY" "History"

                                  @{b}History@{ub}



 · v1.0   08 September 1996
           - First release.

 · v1.1   12 September 1996
          - Fixed WBIcon loading problem
          - Removed external WBIcon loading program from StartupPlus & Prefs
          - No longer have to have a window at startupp time
          - Added Ask Window
          - Added More Tooltypes

 · V1.11  01 October 1996
          - Only Mark Ritter got a copy to test.

 · v1.2   28 October 1996
          - No changes to the main program.

 · v1.3   10 January 1997
          - No longer activates the window at startup.
          - Increased icon display size to: width 90 pixels and height 66
            pixels

 · v1.4   21 February 1997
          - Added a menu bar to make editing the MUI Interface easier.
          - Reimplemented the Ask window and fixed all the bugs that came
            with it
          - Major over haul on the code.
          - Faster Execution. If you want even faster execution disable
            the window
          - Fully Localized
          - Menu Bar added to the Ask Window
          - You can now abort the execution sequence when ever you want
          - MUI Settings and MUI About added
          - You are now able to remove a program that you normaly load from
            the Execution Sequence. Say if you want to play a game that
            can't be run with Virtual Memory.
          - LowLevel RawKey Handelng
          - Ability to change the datafile at startup.
          - Replaced the WBStart-Handler with WBStarter.library and
            DOSPath.library

 · v1.5   1 September 1997
          - Changed the look of the GUI (MUI)
          - Improved the Error handeling
          - Changed the Keyfile
          - Added wildcard handeling to only locate SUP datafiles
          - Now Compiled in SAS C 5.57


